   Police Officer
   Tenure Eligible
   Application must be submitted by March 31, 2002
   shifts vary
   COMPENSATION Starting Salary: $36, 909 per year Tenure-Eligible

   SHIFTS Rotating Shiftwork

   MINIMUM REQUIREMENTS HS Grad/GED - Ability to pass police testing -
   Meet AZPOST pre-employment drug use standards - Live within a 15-mile
   radius of downtown Flagstaff (within 3 months of hire) - Possess valid
   Arizona driver's license.

   You may contact the Flagstaff Human Resources Division to have a Police
   Recruitment Package mailed to you. Please call (928)779-7698 or email:
   human.resources@ci.flagstaff.az.us

