   EQUIPMENT OPERATOR II
   $15.93 per hour
   Hours are determined by storm conditions
   Temporary position. Requires front-end loader experience. Position
   involves plowing and stacking of cul-de-sacs. Must have a valid Arizona
   Driver's Licence. This position works on an on-call basis during
   snowstorms. We are seeking individuals who have the flexibility to be
   called in on very short notice, and be willing to work late night hours
   and long shifts as determined by storm conditions.

