   CDL EQUIPMENT OPERATOR II
   $15.93 per hour
   Hours are determined by storm conditions.
   Temporary position. Requires Class B CDL and ability to operate heavy
   equipment and perform manual labor in adverse weather. Please include a
   MVD driving record from the last three years with your application. CDL
   drivers may also be subject to drug/alcohol testing. Position works on
   an on-call basis during snowstorms. Seeking dependable individuals who
   have the flexibility to be called in on very short notice and be
   willing to work late night hours and long shifts as determined by storm
   conditions.

